cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CY 

The paper focuses on Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques to predict trends in the stock market using news headlines. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with NLP and information retrieval. The paper also uses statistical and deep learning models, which are covered in cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of embeddings is also mentioned, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with financial data, which could be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
